phpMp version 2 beta 2
======================

Description:
------------
A web-based client for mpd, written in PHP. (http://www.php.net)

Requirements:
-------------
-mpd
-apache
-php 4.1 or higher
-php with gd support for graphical sliders

Installation:
-------------
Download phpMp2 and extract into a directory on your webserver:

 $tar xjvf phpmp2-b2.tar.bz2

Alternatively, you can use subversion to get the latest bleeding-edge version:

 $svn checkout https://theory5.chem.pitt.edu/svn/mpd/phpMp2/trunk phpMp2

Edit config.php; This file contains numerous configuration options described in
the comments in the file.

Usage:
------
Surf to the location of the extracted tarball with your web browser.

Credits:
